        <div class="flex">
          <div>
            <h4 class="subsection__header">Built Around You</h4>
            <p>
              <b>Your website should feel like home</b>. I don’t use templates—I
              listen, adapt, and build something that reflects your values, your
              voice, and your vision.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="subsection__header">Gentle Guidance, Clear Direction</h4>
            <p>
              <b>Not sure where to start? That’s okay</b>. I’ll walk you through
              the process step by step, helping you shape your content and
              structure with clarity and care.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="subsection__header">Sustainable by Nature</h4>
            <p>
              <b>Good design lasts</b>. I build with clean code, ethical tools,
              and long-term thinking—so your site grows with you, not against
              you.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <%- include('./partials/svggrow.ejs') %>
        <h3 x-data x-intersect.once="grow()" class="thing">Grow</h3>
        <div class="flex">
          <div>
            <h4 class="subsection__header">Responsive & Reliable</h4>
            <p>
              <b>I’m here when you need me</b>. Fast replies, flexible
              solutions, and a collaborative spirit mean you’re never left
              waiting or wondering.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="subsection__header">
              Creative, But Never Overcomplicated
            </h4>
            <p>
              <b>Your site should be beautiful—and make sense</b>. I balance
              design with usability, so your visitors feel welcome and your
              message lands.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="subsection__header">Calm, not Chaos</h4>
            <p>
              <b>Tech doesn’t have to be stressful</b>. I make the process feel
              smooth and human, so you can focus on your mission while I handle
              the mechanics.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <%- include('./partials/svgflourish.ejs') %>
        <h3 x-data x-intersect.once="flourish()" class="thing">Flourish</h3>
        <div class="flex">
          <div>
            <h4 class="subsection__header">Clarity over Clutter</h4>
            <p>
              <b>You don’t need to have it all figured out</b>. I help you
              organize your ideas, shape your message, and create a site that
              speaks with purpose.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="subsection__header">Rooted in Authenticity</h4>
            <p>
              <b>You’re not just another client</b>. I work with people who
              care—and I make sure their websites reflect that care in every
              detail.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="subsection__header">
              Made for Small Teams & Solo Founders
            </h4>
            <p>
              <b>I get your world.</b> I know what it’s like to wear many hats,
              and I build sites that support your work without adding
              complexity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
